<P>A TREATY Between the Government of <HI>New-Jer&s;ey,</HI> AND THE <HI>INDIANS,</HI> Inhabiting the &s;everal Parts of &s;aid Province, Held at <HI>CROSWICKS,</HI> In the County of <HI>BURLINGTON</HI> On <HI>Thur&s;day</HI> and <HI>Friday</HI> the <HI>eighth</HI> and <HI>ninth</HI> Day of <HI>January,</HI> 1756.</P>
<P><HI>PHILADELPHIA:</HI> Printed by WILLIAM BRADFORD, Printer to the Province of <HI>New-Jer&s;ey.</HI></P>
</DIV1>
