<BODY>
<DIV1 TYPE="day's proceedings">
<PB REF="007688_0002_102D998DD94F4750">
<HEAD>A TREATY between the Government of <HI>New-Jer&s;ey,</HI> AND THE <HI>INDIANS.</HI></HEAD>
<P><HI>Thur&s;day</HI> the <HI>eighth</HI> Day of <HI>January,</HI> 1756.</P>
<P>THE Commi&s;&s;ioners and the following <HI>Indians</HI> being met.</P>
<LIST>
<HEAD>The Names of the <HI>Indians.</HI></HEAD>
<ITEM><LIST>
<HEAD>Cranberry <HI>Indians,</HI> who pa&s;s by the <HI>Engli&s;h</HI> Names.</HEAD>
